						               													<description>The Little Prince board game inspired by classic novel book + coaching concept + positive parenting concept. This game allow you to create safety environment to play and learn parent philosophy quality time with a group of 2-4 players that you can choose yourself. To share, discussion become &amp;quot;The Old New World&amp;quot; of your own.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;For the game mechanic is very simple for understand and play. Which life the space for sharing and learn each other via playing game.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;For the developer (Thailand Coaching Institute and Learning From Boardgames) believe this game will help you to create &amp;quot;The Quality Time&amp;quot; and visualize how become parents the way you choose to be&amp;#10;&amp;#10;You may choose you boss and design your career path. But for you children, they can't choose their parents or quit being your child.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The player try to collect the card set to convert to the Quote Card to gain more points. and the most point is the winner.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The Color in the game;&amp;#10;1) Red (Rose) 1 point&amp;#10;2) Yellow (Fox) 2 points&amp;#10;3) Blue (The Little Prince) 3 points&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The set of Red Yellow and blue able to covert 1 Quote Card (that contain 10 points). Alternatively, 5 reds or 4 yellow or 3 blue able to ruin the black (Snake) that contain -5 points from their score.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;4) White (Sheep) 4 points:the set of 2 white able to convert 1 quote card (that contain 10 points)&amp;#10;&amp;#10;5) Black (Snake) - 5 points: The set of 3 black are guarantee you win the game.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
